    <p>
        This Privacy Policy explains the privacy practices of the mobile game named <strong>Don’t Touch The Chicken</strong>.
        This policy applies when you download, install, open, use, or interact with advertisements displayed within the game.
    </p>

    <p>
        Don’t Touch The Chicken is designed as a simple mobile game. The game does not include user account creation,
        membership, subscriptions, in-app purchases, payment collection, chat features, social media login, user profile
        creation, or any feature that directly requests personal information from users.
    </p>

    <p>
        The game only displays banner advertisements. These advertisements are served by Google AdMob and may involve
        limited technical data processing by Google and its advertising partners. As the developer, we do not directly
        request or collect personal information such as name, surname, email address, phone number, physical address,
        payment information, username, password, photo, contact list, microphone recording, camera image, or similar
        personal data from users.
    </p>

    <div class="notice">
        <p>
            This policy is intended to describe a game that uses banner advertisements only. If future versions of the
            game add analytics, subscriptions, in-app purchases, user accounts, push notifications, or additional SDKs,
            this Privacy Policy should be updated before those features are released.
        </p>
