    </p>
    <p>This policy applies to the following situations:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Downloading and installing the game on your device</li>
        <li>Opening and playing the game</li>
        <li>Viewing banner advertisements within the game</li>
        <li>Clicking on or interacting with banner advertisements</li>
        <li>Contacting us through the app store page, support email, or privacy policy links</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
        This policy does not fully control the data processing activities of third-party advertising providers, app
        stores, device manufacturers, operating system providers, or external websites linked through advertisements.
        The privacy policies and terms of use of those third parties apply to their own services.
    </p>

